#. type: Title ==
#, no-wrap
msgid "LINSTOR Volumes in Docker"
msgstr "DockerのLINSTORボリューム"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"indexterm:[docker]This chapter describes LINSTOR volumes in Docker as "
"managed by the https://github.com/LINBIT/linstor-docker-volume[LINSTOR "
"Docker Volume Plugin]."
msgstr ""
"indexterm:[docker]この章では https://github.com/LINBIT/linstor-docker-"
"volume[LINSTOR Docker Volume Plugin] で管理されているDockerのLINSTORボリュー"
"ムについて説明します。"

#. type: Title ===
#, no-wrap
msgid "Docker Overview"
msgstr "Dockerの概要"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"_Docker_ is a platform for developing, shipping, and running applications in "
"the form of Linux containers. For stateful applications that require data "
"persistence, Docker supports the use of persistent _volumes_ and "
"_volume_drivers_."
msgstr ""
"_Docker_ は、Linuxコンテナの形でアプリケーションを開発、出荷、および実行する"
"ためのプラットフォームです。データの永続化を必要とするステートフルアプリケー"
"ションのために、Dockerは永続的な _volumes_ と _volume_drivers_ の使用をサポー"
"トします。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The https://github.com/LINBIT/linstor-docker-volume[LINSTOR Docker Volume "
"Plugin] is a volume driver that provisions persistent volumes from a LINSTOR "
"cluster for Docker containers."
msgstr ""
"https://github.com/LINBIT/linstor-docker-volume[LINSTOR Docker Volume "
"Plugin] は、LINSTORクラスタから永続的ボリュームをプロビジョニングするDockerコ"
"ンテナ用のボリュームドライバです。"

#. type: Title ===
#, no-wrap
msgid "LINSTOR Plugin for Docker Installation"
msgstr "Dockerインストール用のLINSTORプラグイン"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To install the `linstor-docker-volume` package provided by LINBIT, you'll "
"need to have LINBIT's `drbd-9.0` repository enabled. Once enabled, use your "
"package manager to install the `linstor-docker-volume` package:"
msgstr ""
"LINBITが提供する `linstor-docker-volume` パッケージをインストールするには、"
"LINBITの `drbd-9.0` リポジトリを有効にする必要があります。有効になったら、"
"パッケージマネージャを使って `linstor-docker-volume` パッケージをインストール"
"してください。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "# yum install linstor-docker-volume\n"
msgstr "# yum install linstor-docker-volume\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "  -- OR --\n"
msgstr "  -- または --\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "# apt install linstor-docker-volume\n"
msgstr "# apt install linstor-docker-volume\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Alternatively, you can build and install from source:"
msgstr "あるいは、ソースからビルドしてインストールすることもできます。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# git clone https://github.com/LINBIT/linstor-docker-volume\n"
"# cd ./linstor-docker-volume\n"
"# make\n"
"  ..snip..\n"
"# make doc\n"
"  ..snip..\n"
"# make install\n"
"  ..snip..\n"
msgstr ""
"# git clone https://github.com/LINBIT/linstor-docker-volume\n"
"# cd ./linstor-docker-volume\n"
"# make\n"
"  ..snip..\n"
"# make doc\n"
"  ..snip..\n"
"# make install\n"
"  ..snip..\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Once installed, _enable_ and _start_ the `linstor-docker-volume.socket` and "
"`linstor-docker-volume.service` via `systemd`:"
msgstr ""
"インストールが完了したら `systemd` で `linstor-docker-volume.socket` と "
"`linstor-docker-volume.service` を有効にして起動します。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "# systemctl enable linstor-docker-volume.socket linstor-docker-volume.service --now\n"
msgstr "# systemctl enable linstor-docker-volume.socket linstor-docker-volume.service --now\n"

#. type: Title ===
#, no-wrap
msgid "LINSTOR Plugin for Docker Configuration"
msgstr "Docker設定用のLINSTORプラグイン"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"As the plugin has to communicate to the LINSTOR controller via the LINSTOR "
"python library, we must tell the plugin where to find the LINSTOR Controller "
"node in it's configuration file:"
msgstr ""
"プラグインはLINSTOR pythonライブラリを介してLINSTORコントローラと通信する必要"
"があるので、プラグインの設定ファイルでLINSTORコントローラノードの場所を指定す"
"る必要があります。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cat /etc/linstor/docker-volume.conf\n"
"[global]\n"
"controllers = linstor://hostnameofcontroller\n"
msgstr ""
"# cat /etc/linstor/docker-volume.conf\n"
"[global]\n"
"controllers = linstor://hostnameofcontroller\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"It is also possible to set all of the command line options found in `man "
"linstor-docker-volume` in the `docker-volume.conf`. For example:"
msgstr ""
"`docker-volume.conf` の `man linstor-docker-volume` にあるすべてのコマンドラ"
"インオプションを設定することも可能です。例えば："

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cat /etc/linstor/docker-volume.conf\n"
"[global]\n"
"storagepool = thin-lvm\n"
"fs = ext4\n"
"fsopts = -E discard\n"
"size = 100MB\n"
"replicas = 2\n"
"nodes = alpha,bravo,charlie\n"
msgstr ""
"# cat /etc/linstor/docker-volume.conf\n"
"[global]\n"
"storagepool = thin-lvm\n"
"fs = ext4\n"
"fsopts = -E discard\n"
"size = 100MB\n"
"replicas = 2\n"
"nodes = alpha,bravo,charlie\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"If neither _replicas_ or _nodes_ is defined, the default of _replicas_ will "
"be used, which is two diskful replicas. If both _replicas_ and _nodes_ are "
"defined, _nodes_ will be used and _replicas_ will be ignored."
msgstr ""
"_replicas_ も _nodes_ も定義されていない場合は、デフォルトの _replicas_ が使"
"用されます。これは2つのディスクフルの複製です。 _replicas_ と _nodes_ の両方"
"が定義されている場合、_nodes_ が使用され _replicas_ は無視されます。"

#. type: Title ===
#, no-wrap
msgid "Example Usage"
msgstr "使用例"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The following are some examples of how you might use the LINSTOR Docker "
"Volume Plugin.  In the following we expect a cluster consisting of three "
"nodes (alpha, bravo, and charlie)."
msgstr ""
"以下は、LINSTOR Docker Volume Pluginの使用例です。以下では、3つのノード "
"(alpha, bravo, charlie) からなるクラスターを想定しています。"

#. type: Title ====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Example 1 - typical docker pattern"
msgstr "例1  - 典型的なdockerパターン"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "On node alpha:"
msgstr "ノードalpha上:"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ docker volume create -d linstor \\\n"
"             --opt fs=xfs --opt size=200 lsvol\n"
"$ docker run -it --rm --name=cont \\\n"
"             -v lsvol:/data --volume-driver=linstor busybox sh\n"
"$ root@cont: echo \"foo\" > /data/test.txt\n"
"$ root@cont: exit\n"
msgstr ""
"$ docker volume create -d linstor \\\n"
"             --opt fs=xfs --opt size=200 lsvol\n"
"$ docker run -it --rm --name=cont \\\n"
"             -v lsvol:/data --volume-driver=linstor busybox sh\n"
"$ root@cont: echo \"foo\" > /data/test.txt\n"
"$ root@cont: exit\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "On node bravo:"
msgstr "ノードbravo上:"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ docker run -it --rm --name=cont \\\n"
"             -v lsvol:/data --volume-driver=linstor busybox sh\n"
"$ root@cont: cat /data/test.txt\n"
"  foo\n"
"$ root@cont: exit\n"
"$ docker volume rm lsvol\n"
msgstr ""
"$ docker run -it --rm --name=cont \\\n"
"             -v lsvol:/data --volume-driver=linstor busybox sh\n"
"$ root@cont: cat /data/test.txt\n"
"  foo\n"
"$ root@cont: exit\n"
"$ docker volume rm lsvol\n"

#. type: Title ====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Example 2 - one diskfull assignment by name, two nodes diskless"
msgstr "例2 - ホスト指定で1つのディスクフル割り当て、2つのディスクレスノード"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "$ docker volume create -d linstor --opt hosts=bravo lsvol\n"
msgstr "$ docker volume create -d linstor --opt hosts=bravo lsvol\n"

#. type: Title ====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Example 3 - one diskfull assignment, no matter where, two nodes diskless"
msgstr "例3 - どこかに1つのディスクフル割り当て、2つのディスクレスノード"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "$ docker volume create -d linstor --opt replicas=1 lsvol\n"
msgstr "$ docker volume create -d linstor --opt replicas=1 lsvol\n"

#. type: Title ====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Example 4 - two diskfull assignments by name, charlie diskless"
msgstr "例4 - ホスト指定で2つのディスクフル割り当て、charlie はディスクレス"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "$ docker volume create -d linstor --opt hosts=alpha,bravo lsvol\n"
msgstr "$ docker volume create -d linstor --opt hosts=alpha,bravo lsvol\n"

#. type: Title ====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Example 5 - two diskfull assignments, no matter where, one node diskless"
msgstr "例5 - どこかに2つのディスクフル割り当て、1つのディスクレスノード"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "$ docker volume create -d linstor --opt replicas=2 lsvol\n"
msgstr "$ docker volume create -d linstor --opt replicas=2 lsvol\n"

#. type: Title ====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Example 6 - using curl without docker, useful for developers"
msgstr "例6 - dockerでなくcurlを使う、開発者向け"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ curl --unix-socket /run/docker/plugins/linstor.sock \\\n"
"          -X POST -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"\n"
"          -d '{\"Name\":\"linstorvol\"}' http://localhost/VolumeDriver.List\n"
msgstr ""
"$ curl --unix-socket /run/docker/plugins/linstor.sock \\\n"
"          -X POST -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"\n"
"          -d '{\"Name\":\"linstorvol\"}' http://localhost/VolumeDriver.List\n"
